			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: The Secrets of Power Leveling from 20-50<a name="22099"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 18 04 11:36 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Find some social mobs.  Grab a whole lot of them.
<br />

<br />
Twist some AE damage, not enough to kill em all, but enough to take em to about 25% (depends on mobs)
<br />

<br />
wait for DOT to wear off, then Fade.  Mobs will forget you damaged them.
<br />

<br />
Sing Selo's assonante strane (Slow and Snare, no damage) to get aggro again, and twist in a DS.
<br />
Have lower Bard wade in and sing one pulse of CoD to do damage to them all, then be prepared to run like h*ll
<br />
Hopefully the mobs will still be beating on you, the Damage they take from the DS will near kill them, the other bard chases them down as they run and gets the exp.
<br />

<br />
If the mobs are blue to the other bard, he/she might be able to twist in AE damage songs and AE them all.
<br />

<br />
Either way, you do mot of the killing, the other bard gets the exp
<br />
</span></td>
